headers {
  User-Agent: OpenShock/Bruno
}

docs {
  # OpenShock API
  
  REST API for the OpenShock platform.
  
  ## Authentication
  
  Set `API_TOKEN` or `HUB_TOKEN` in your environment variables.
  Auth is configured per-folder so requests inherit automatically.
  
  ## API Versions
  
  Endpoints use the latest available version (V2 where available, V1 otherwise).
  Superseded V1 endpoints are in the Deprecated/ folder.
}
